Fake News Detection
Description: This dataset includes text data labeled as either “Fake” or “Real” news.
Use Case: Build a classifier to distinguish between fake and real news articles.
Columns: title, text, label
Why It’s Suitable: It’s a straightforward binary classification task with rich textual data, allowing you to practice feature extraction and classification.
Link: https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/clmentbisaillon/fake-and-real-news-dataset
